author: arkurth
msg: Fixed recusion problem with Linux init and firewall modules. They can't call $self->sub directly to access the OS. Instead, $self->os->sub must be called.
Added firewall.pm which iptables.pm inherits from.
Fixed recursion issue in utils.pm::get_computer_nathost_info if the computer and NAT host are the same computer.
